Public Class CollectionNavigationBuilder Implements IInfrastructure(Of InternalRelationshipBuilder)

summary.para: Provides a simple API for configuring a relationship where configuration began on an end of the relationship with a collection that contains instances of another entity type.
Instances of this class are returned from methods when using the API and it is not designed to be directly constructed in your application code.

summary.para: Configures this as a one-to-many relationship.

Note that calling this method with no parameters will explicitly configure this side of the relationship to use no navigation property, even if such a property exists on the entity type. If the navigation property is to be used, then it must be specified.

Docs.returns: An object to further configure the relationship.
